Job/Team Function:
The Smarter Working Programme is enabling new ways of working across the Home Office through transformation of people, technology and workplace whilst reducing cost to the taxpayer.
• People – helping people move to new, more flexible ways of working that suit both the individual and the business;
• Technology – equipping people with modern IT and communications tools, supporting mobility and collaboration;
• Workspace – modernising our workplaces to meet future business needs while reducing cost to the taxpayer.
